				Open an ISA and make use of your ISA allowance for the current and following tax year.
			</h2>

			<div class="g-typography g-typography--career" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
				<p>
					Opening a stock and shares ISA account offers you a tax efficient way to save and grow your money. Because when you invest through your ISA account, any profits from those investment are free of UK Capital Gains tax. 
				</p>
				<p>
					You can invest up to £20,000 a year, you can select from a wide range of stocks, shares and exchange traded funds, and you can do that in one ISA or a set of different ISAs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="g-title-devider g-title-devider--important">
				Important information
			</div>

			<div class="g-typography g-typography--career">
				<p>
