					To transfer your ISA to ITI Capital, simply email <a href="#" class="g-link">ISAs@iticapital.com</a> requesting a transfer pack and one of our dedicated team members will be in touch with you regarding the next steps.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="g-typography g-typography--pl-xl-32">
