		<div class="private-section-content">
			<div class="g-typography">
				<h2 class="g-title-light">
					You can shelter up to £20,000 in any tax year in an ITI Capital ISA
				</h2>
				<p>
					Got other ISAs?  No problem. Simply consolidate all of your ISAs into one place by transferring them easily into ITI Capital and still maintain each year’s tax-free gains, making it easy to invest in future years ISA allowances.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
