				<h2>
					Is Stocks and Shares ISA <br>suitable for you?
				</h2>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="private-section-content">
			<div class="g-typography">
				<p>
					We have a wealth of experience and market knowledge to help you get the most from your finances. We use a tried and tested approach to ensure that we manage all our clients’ financial affairs efficiently, responsibly and ethically. 
				</p>
				<p>
					If you are unsure whether a Stocks and Shares ISA is suitable for you, please get in touch with our ISA team today at <a href="#" class="g-link">ISAs@iticapital.com</a> and a member of our team will be happy to assist you.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

