				Fees
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="private-section-content private-section-content--nobg">
			<div class="g-typography g-typography--pb0">
				<p>
					Its free to set up an ISA account and you only pay trading or smart portfolio fees when you start to invest. Email <a href="#" class="g-link">ISAs@iticapital.com</a> for further details. 
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
